00:23:00.660 --> 00:23:03.000
She'll just look at anyone and fall in love!

310
00:23:03.590 --> 00:23:05.250
Oh gosh, I hate that.

311
00:23:05.250 --> 00:23:08.440
Exactly, I'm a really easy woman, Right?

312
00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:13.520
That time was the best. When she fell in love with the man in front of the studio in three seconds.

313
00:23:13.520 --> 00:23:16.450
- How handsome was he? 
 - Hey.

