396
00:29:28.790 --> 00:29:32.600
- It's not that fishy. Try it. 
 - Yes, of course.

397
00:29:37.750 --> 00:29:41.400
- I'll bring it to you. 
 - Sounds tasty.

398
00:29:50.530 --> 00:29:54.430
- How was it? 
 - It... was good.

399
00:29:54.430 --> 00:29:57.200
- I enjoyed it. 
 - Yeah!

400
00:30:05.710 --> 00:30:09.730
Okay... the mackerel gratin is here. 
<i>[Pororo Lightning Interview!!]</i>

401
00:30:09.730 --> 00:30:12.510
- Enjoy it. 
 - I will.

402
00:30:44.760 --> 00:30:46.860
<i>If you drink this, we're dating. Okay?</i>

403
00:30:50.150 --> 00:30:52.480
<i>What if I don't drink it?</i>

404
00:30:53.840 --> 00:30:57.370
<i>Then nothing happens between us.</i>

405
00:31:13.210 --> 00:31:15.000
