406
00:31:35.860 --> 00:31:38.190
There you are!

407
00:32:09.260 --> 00:32:12.020
<i>[112] </i>

408
00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:26.960
Mom?

409
00:32:41.730 --> 00:32:43.640
Hey, you!

410
00:32:49.080 --> 00:32:50.760
- You're back? 
 - Whoa!

411
00:32:56.190 --> 00:32:57.950
What are you doing here?

412
00:32:57.950 --> 00:33:00.050
I moved here yesterday.

413
00:33:00.050 --> 00:33:03.530
- Who moved in? To our house? 
 - Yeah.

414
00:33:03.530 --> 00:33:06.360
Why would you? Who are you to be moving into my house?

415
00:33:06.360 --> 00:33:09.260
I'm a new tenant here now.

416
00:33:11.700 --> 00:33:13.860
What nonsense are you saying?

417
00:33:17.120 --> 00:33:18.960
