420
00:33:24.380 --> 00:33:26.970
You must be tired. Let's have some breakfast.

421
00:33:26.970 --> 00:33:28.770
That's all right, I don't need any food.

422
00:33:28.770 --> 00:33:34.810
Hey! You've got to be kidding me. Get out!

423
00:33:46.130 --> 00:33:48.570
I don't have anywhere else to go.

424
00:33:49.430 --> 00:33:52.210
Did you lose your house to Seo Jungwon?

425
00:33:52.210 --> 00:33:55.690
Are you joking? She was at fault. Why would I lose the house?

426
00:33:55.690 --> 00:33:58.410
She insisted on paying back all the borrowed money, too.

427
00:33:58.410 --> 00:34:01.210
At least she had a conscience. Terrible girl.

428
00:34:01.210 --> 00:34:05.350
She was terrible... How could she do that to me?

429
00:34:05.350 --> 00:34:07.730
You have no conscience.

430
00:34:07.730 --> 00:34:12.040
How can you just chatter away at me, after turning up for the first time in five years,

431
00:34:12.950 --> 00:34:16.120
while looking right at me as if this was nothing strange?

432
00:34:21.970 --> 00:34:24.570
Then I'll talk without looking at you.

433
00:34:26.810 --> 00:34:32.440
To be honest, it's because I don't think I can stand living alone with my kid.

434
00:34:32.440 --> 00:34:35.440
Mom and Dad want me to return to the States.

435
00:34:35.440 --> 00:34:38.590
Where?

436
00:34:39.550 --> 00:34:43.830
You're all I have left, my friend.

437
00:34:43.830 --> 00:34:45.610
After all this time,

438
00:34:45.610 --> 00:34:50.320
after cutting me out of your life because Seo Jungwon said she hated me,

439
00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:51.930
you come back acting as if nothing happened

440
00:34:51.930 --> 00:34:56.300
because she left you.

441
00:34:58.300 --> 00:35:01.880
