442
00:35:01.880 --> 00:35:06.280
Have a look at her face, and then we can talk it over again.

443
00:35:20.390 --> 00:35:23.610
Hi! So you're Doha. My goodness,

444
00:35:23.610 --> 00:35:26.810
so cute!

445
00:35:31.490 --> 00:35:34.190
Do you not wash your kid?

446
00:35:35.090 --> 00:35:39.940
Kids are supposed to be messy when they eat. That's perfectly normal.

447
00:35:39.940 --> 00:35:42.060
Why is her baby bottle so small?

448
00:35:42.060 --> 00:35:46.160
If she's 8 months old, you have to get her one that's 240 ml!

449
00:35:46.160 --> 00:35:49.590
How did you know she's 8 months old?

450
00:35:49.590 --> 00:35:53.330
How did you end up with a dad like that? Right?

451
00:35:53.330 --> 00:35:58.850
You poor little thing. Our poor little Doha.

452
00:35:58.850 --> 00:36:01.250
Isn't my Doha super cute?

453
00:36:01.250 --> 00:36:06.230
Yes. Since she's so cute, I'll give you a day. Pack up and leave by tomorrow.

454
00:36:06.230 --> 00:36:10.080
Even if she's this cute? And just turned 8 months old?

455
00:36:10.080 --> 00:36:12.090
We have nowhere to go.

456
00:36:12.090 --> 00:36:17.850
Okay then. My deadline is by 2:00 a.m. You can leave Doha here, but get out before I'm back.

457
00:36:17.850 --> 00:36:20.810
I'm going to report you; give me back my daughter.

458
00:36:24.970 --> 00:36:28.290
Isn't that lady scary?

459
00:36:28.290 --> 00:36:30.390
This is all because of you! Don't cry.

460
00:36:45.920 --> 00:36:48.600
Mom, are you Jaeyoung's mom?

461
00:36:50.070 --> 00:36:53.050
That poor thing is practically a beggar,

462
00:36:53.050 --> 00:36:55.030
<i>I didn't feel too good about his situation.</i>

463
00:36:55.030 --> 00:36:57.660
You only need to add one extra pair of chopsticks on the table,

464
00:36:57.660 --> 00:36:59.730
<i>and check if he's feeding his kid well.</i>

465
00:36:59.730 --> 00:37:02.840
I heard all Jaeyoung does is drink. Make sure he doesn't.

466
00:37:02.840 --> 00:37:04.000
You can't even do that much?

467
00:37:04.000 --> 00:37:06.300
Did he become a patient after he got divorced?

468
00:37:06.300 --> 00:37:09.660
