469
00:37:09.660 --> 00:37:13.470
Okay, I'll send Jaeyoung out. You leave, too.

470
00:37:13.470 --> 00:37:14.780
Why should I?

471
00:37:14.780 --> 00:37:17.260
It's not your house, it's mine.

472
00:37:17.260 --> 00:37:19.730
<i>You think you're the homeowner, even though you're not even paying the rent? </i>

473
00:37:19.730 --> 00:37:23.030
